Comment:
I don't understand... Why all the kids' games, the cartoon indie games fit for iPhones, the CGI trailers that falsely represent a game we know very little to nothing about, the absence of gameplay, the shortest update on XCloud and a pointless video diary of the specs for the next Xbox which most already know about?


We look forward to this every year, and we hear that Microsoft promises the biggest and best E3 to date... And yet we get this?  Very disappointing for most (including me obv) and could have saved most a couple of hours by simply putting this in an episode of 'This week on Xbox'.
